<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 16:10:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区向加沙捐赠数十吨援助物资，但以色列阻止其进入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-arab-community-donated-dozens-of-tons-of-aid-to-gaza-but-israel-blocks-its-entry/00000191-a8a6-d3dd-a991-a8be2e7d0000</link><description>以色列军队声称，只有来自国外的捐赠或从约旦河西岸的商人那里购买的援助物资才能进入加沙地带</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:10:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-arab-community-donated-dozens-of-tons-of-aid-to-gaza-but-israel-blocks-its-entry/00000191-a8a6-d3dd-a991-a8be2e7d0000</guid></item><item><title>“嗨，我是李比。我想告诉你我的兄弟赫什·戈德堡-波林是加沙的人质”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-09-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hi-its-leebie-i-wanted-to-tell-you-my-brother-hersh-is-a-hostage-in-gaza/00000191-b215-d27a-a1b3-ba3510410000</link><description>10 月 7 日三周后，赫什·戈德堡-波林的妹妹联系了《国土报》的阿米尔·蒂邦，他本人也是哈马斯袭击的幸存者。已故人质的家人直到最后一刻仍保持乐观</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:07:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-09-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hi-its-leebie-i-wanted-to-tell-you-my-brother-hersh-is-a-hostage-in-gaza/00000191-b215-d27a-a1b3-ba3510410000</guid></item><item><title>“社区对此非常渴望”：以色列南部最大的医院开设了一个新的 LGBTQ 诊所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-the-shadow-of-war-southern-israels-largest-hospital-gets-a-new-lgbtq-clinic/00000191-9d90-df07-a3b9-fddc232b0000</link><description>当 Inbar Izhak 提议在索罗卡医院为酷儿社区开设第一家妇科诊所时，她得到了那些想要安全、知情护理的人们的“疯狂顺风”。对于诊所的首席医生 Iris Shoham 来说，这项工作充满了灵性：“就像上帝在房间里一样”</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 13:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-the-shadow-of-war-southern-israels-largest-hospital-gets-a-new-lgbtq-clinic/00000191-9d90-df07-a3b9-fddc232b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的六名人质是怎么死的？阿拉伯世界无法决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/how-did-the-six-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-die-the-arab-world-cant-decide/00000191-b227-dd49-afd3-b77774350000</link><description>社交媒体上的猜测甚嚣尘上，有人说哈马斯处决人质是针对以色列社会的心理战的一部分，而另一些人则转而否认，将人质的死亡归咎于以色列</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/how-did-the-six-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-die-the-arab-world-cant-decide/00000191-b227-dd49-afd3-b77774350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军官员：如果没有美国的援助，以色列几个月后无法与加沙作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/without-u-s-aid-israel-would-have-struggled-to-fight-in-gaza-beyond-a-few-months/00000191-aec2-d875-a3bb-aed7e2e30000</link><description>一名高级空军军官还告诉国土报，国际合作挫败了伊朗 4 月份的袭击，并在 8 月份对真主党发动了先发制人的打击，以色列努力减少这种依赖</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/without-u-s-aid-israel-would-have-struggled-to-fight-in-gaza-beyond-a-few-months/00000191-aec2-d875-a3bb-aed7e2e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方公布照片证明本-格维尔和助手受邀发射先进武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-release-pictures-proving-ben-gvir-and-aides-invited-to-fire-advanced-weapons/00000191-b22d-d835-aff3-b3ed98c00000</link><description>2023 年 8 月，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔 (Itamar Ben-Gvir) 参观了一个特种部队的训练基地，他、他的参谋长和驾驶员在那里被允许操作先进武器，这是一项非同寻常的举动。只有《国土报》向法庭请愿才披露了这一非同寻常事件的照片。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:00:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-release-pictures-proving-ben-gvir-and-aides-invited-to-fire-advanced-weapons/00000191-b22d-d835-aff3-b3ed98c00000</guid></item><item><title>除非周日的强烈抗议活动继续下去，否则以色列血淋淋的内阁不会停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-blood-soaked-cabinet-wont-stop-if-sundays-protests-were-a-one-off/00000191-b1ec-d67d-a7f5-fbee8a3f0000</link><description>就像 10 月 7 日之后的几个小时一样，越来越明显的是，内塔尼亚胡完全失去了功能，他的个人和政治生存比人质的生命重要一千倍。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 11:43:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-blood-soaked-cabinet-wont-stop-if-sundays-protests-were-a-one-off/00000191-b1ec-d67d-a7f5-fbee8a3f0000</guid></item><item><title>球迷因国歌发生冲突后，阿拉伯以色列领先足球队的比赛被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/leading-arab-israeli-soccer-teams-game-scrapped-after-fans-clash-over-national-anthem/00000191-b21c-d93f-a5bb-b31edaf20000</link><description>Bnei Sakhnin 的球员在球迷与贝尔谢巴夏普尔队的球迷发生冲突后拒绝返回球场</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 11:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/leading-arab-israeli-soccer-teams-game-scrapped-after-fans-clash-over-national-anthem/00000191-b21c-d93f-a5bb-b31edaf20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大罢工：谁在工作，谁不在工作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/israels-general-strike-whos-working-and-whos-not/00000191-b17e-d123-a1dd-b17f77390000</link><description>为支持签署人质协议的呼吁而发起的总罢工于周一早上开始</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 07:07:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/israels-general-strike-whos-working-and-whos-not/00000191-b17e-d123-a1dd-b17f77390000</guid></item><item><title>塞尔维亚对以色列的武器销售激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/serbian-arms-sales-to-israel-spike/00000191-acd4-d3dd-a991-acde22540000</link><description>至少有15架来自塞尔维亚的航班降落在以色列空军基地；海关数据显示军火贸易商向以色列出口了价值2300万欧元的武器</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 03:06:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/serbian-arms-sales-to-israel-spike/00000191-acd4-d3dd-a991-acde22540000</guid></item><item><title>人质被处决应该是内塔尼亚胡支持者清算的时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/hostages-execution-should-be-a-moment-of-reckoning-for-netanyahus-supporters/00000191-af8c-d875-a3bb-afdf63bc0000</link><description>公众情绪最终将决定以色列历史上最黑暗的篇章之一现在是否结束，或者我们是否允许自己被内塔尼亚胡及其极右翼盟友拉入深渊</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 03:06:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article/.premium/hostages-execution-should-be-a-moment-of-reckoning-for-netanyahus-supporters/00000191-af8c-d875-a3bb-afdf63bc0000</guid></item><item><title>数千人参加被哈马斯杀害的以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-live/israel-braces-for-general-strike-after-night-of-protests-in-support-of-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b077-d25b-aff7-f4f7214f0005</link><description>内塔尼亚胡将于周一晚上举行新闻发布会 ■ 抗议者呼吁达成人质协议，封锁以色列各地的主要高速公路 ■ 白宫表示，拜登、哈里斯将与谈判团队会面 ■ 警方报告在约旦河西岸定居点外的汽车中发现数十公斤爆炸物</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 03:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-live/israel-braces-for-general-strike-after-night-of-protests-in-support-of-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b077-d25b-aff7-f4f7214f0005</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：尽管人质被谋杀，以色列不会在加沙费城路线上妥协</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-will-not-compromise-on-gazas-philadelphi-route-despite-hostage-murders/00000191-aeff-d875-a3bb-aeff6bc20000</link><description>在安全内阁决定以色列不应从埃及-加沙边境撤军后，官员们正在努力预测在哈马斯囚禁的六名人质被谋杀后停火谈判将如何发展</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 20:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-will-not-compromise-on-gazas-philadelphi-route-despite-hostage-murders/00000191-aeff-d875-a3bb-aeff6bc20000</guid></item><item><title>人质的父亲：“这是一场活生生的噩梦。”如果内塔尼亚胡不完成这件事，就会有更多的尸体”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-09-01/ty-article-podcast/hostages-father-if-netanyahu-doesnt-get-this-done-there-will-be-more-bodies/00000191-ae14-d67c-a3bd-efd72cac0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 19:43:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-09-01/ty-article-podcast/hostages-father-if-netanyahu-doesnt-get-this-done-there-will-be-more-bodies/00000191-ae14-d67c-a3bd-efd72cac0000</guid></item><item><title>六名人质遇害后，以色列各地数十万人集会要求加沙达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/masses-rally-across-israel-demanding-gaza-deal-after-six-hostages-murdered/00000191-ae5b-d67c-a3bd-efdf0bec0000</link><description>“内塔尼亚胡每天都在玩俄罗斯轮盘赌，直到所有人质都死了”：以色列劳工联合会主席呼吁总罢工，数十万人走上街头，要求达成加沙人质协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 19:28:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/masses-rally-across-israel-demanding-gaza-deal-after-six-hostages-murdered/00000191-ae5b-d67c-a3bd-efdf0bec0000</guid></item><item><title>利库德集团高级部长：内塔尼亚胡只会在“街道着火时”推动加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-consults-staff-over-fears-of-mass-israeli-protests-demanding-gaza-cease-fire/00000191-ae85-dd1e-adb5-aecfd4dc0000</link><description>利库德集团一位高级部长表示，“承认这一点令人不快，但内塔尼亚胡只有在街道着火的情况下才会推动达成协议”，并补充道，“现在，他害怕本格维尔和斯莫特里奇，而不是人质家属”</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 18:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-consults-staff-over-fears-of-mass-israeli-protests-demanding-gaza-cease-fire/00000191-ae85-dd1e-adb5-aecfd4dc0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登，是时候说出有关以色列人质的痛苦真相了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-01/ty-article/.highlight/biden-its-time-to-tell-the-painful-truth-about-the-israeli-hostages/00000191-adfd-d67c-a3bd-efff5a5a0000</link><description>目前尚不清楚拜登政府是否能够在这种情况下真正达成协议。但如果做不到，它就欠人质家属一件事，尤其是美国人质家属：说实话，停止允许任何一方使用政治伎俩和操纵</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 17:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-01/ty-article/.highlight/biden-its-time-to-tell-the-painful-truth-about-the-israeli-hostages/00000191-adfd-d67c-a3bd-efff5a5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 331 天：部长表示，内塔尼亚胡拖延协议以拯救他的联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-331-netanyahu-stalling-deal-to-save-his-coalition-says-minister/00000191-ae75-d875-a3bb-ae777bb00001</link><description>以色列国防军取回了 10 月 7 日被哈马斯扣押的六名人质尸体，并补充说，他们最近在以色列军队到达他们之前被处决。 以色列劳工联合会主席周一宣布大罢工，称达成释放人质的协议“是比什么都重要” ■ 三名警察在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生 ■ 战争开始 331 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 17:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-331-netanyahu-stalling-deal-to-save-his-coalition-says-minister/00000191-ae75-d875-a3bb-ae777bb00001</guid></item><item><title>为了抗议内塔尼亚胡的残酷行为，以色列安全负责人是否应该辞职？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-protest-netanyahus-cruelty-should-israels-security-chiefs-resign/00000191-adc0-d95c-a5b5-ffd35e4a0000</link><description>以色列国防军、摩萨德和辛贝特的领导人面临着一个戏剧性的困境：他们是否继续为内塔尼亚胡领导的政府服务，而内塔尼亚胡是一个只致力于自己政治生存的破坏者，因此会与人质的流血事件有牵连？</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-protest-netanyahus-cruelty-should-israels-security-chiefs-resign/00000191-adc0-d95c-a5b5-ffd35e4a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公众的关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/the-israeli-publics-moment-of-truth/00000191-ae1f-d3dd-a991-ae1f75410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 15:19:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/the-israeli-publics-moment-of-truth/00000191-ae1f-d3dd-a991-ae1f75410000</guid></item></channel></rss>